item.title: DeadSec CTF 2023 authors writeups
item.description: YouTube writeups The Youtuber SloppyJoePirates did a Great Job explaining his solutions to one-punch and Popcorn. I would really reccommend checking it out if you are like me and preffer watching things to reading them! You can watch it here ONE PUNCH Idea Being a weeb, one of my favorite anime is One Punch Man. the story of a lonley hero who can destroy anything with a single punch! I took inspiration from this to design the first challenge, one-punch.
